{"tid":224920,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學歷通脹係咩?","createTime":"2017-05-01T11:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T12:57:31.000Z","uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"053e1f651bf0bd1b0d146d78449b9d20fb725740","tid":224920,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"首先,屌臭asso ive o 既風氣,由4月尾至6月中會達至高峰，<br />\n因為班AL面對放榜壓力無從發洩 <br />\n要搵人黎踩下定下個心 <br />\n6月中後會突然水盡鵝飛 <br />\n一黎怕自己會入，留條後路 <br />\n二黎開始迷信，想積下口德 <br />\nAL放榜後，愁雲慘霧 <br />\n班CE仔見狀都唔敢亂屌 <br />\n所以由6月尾至8月 <br />\n情況相若，風氣極低位橫行，如經濟衰退一樣 <br />\n到9月，開學兩三禮拜，新一屆AL CE仔開始有壓力，想搵人踩 <br />\nretake緊o既又想有野俾佢增強信心，又踩 <br />\n讀緊asso ive 跟唔上o個班/讀得唔開心o既，又踩 <br />\n因此9月會有個小陽春，之後橫行，<br />\n12月至1月頭，同2月中，分別都會有個小陽春，因為有假放得閒，同考試迫近，<br />\n壓力愈來愈大，3月至4月頭會一直高位橫行 <br />\n最後又到4月尾高峰 <br />\n年年都如是，歲歲皆如此 <br />\n股市係咁就好囉屌你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/aa/35736_476792358008_831763008_6129412_2944023_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110701041334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Faa%2F35736_476792358008_831763008_6129412_2944023_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110701041334&h=959e573d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由asso ive 轉左屌OU <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54eaf0986107610c42ac7b9be64ba272c97fd74","tid":224920,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"又要積口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130d98dd97933b46b6e6f68693191f1231512e5","tid":224920,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要積口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 厚德-10"}]}